title: "TurbGen â€” Turbulence Generator"
message: >-
  TurbGen generates a time sequence of random Fourier modes via an
  Ornstein-Uhlenbeck (OU) process to drive turbulence in hydrodynamical
  simulation codes. It can also generate single turbulent realisations.
  If you use TurbGen, please cite Federrath et al. (2010) and the ASCL entry.

